high_descs: Turn to face the countertop to the right of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the countertop.
Rinse the knife in the sink, removing it afterwards.
Face the drawer directly below the spatula on the counter.
Put the knife in the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a knife and put it away in a drawer.

high_descs: Take a large step to your right to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife that's in front of you underneath the fork.
Take a step back to your left.
Wash the knife in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn to your left to face the counter.
Open the drawer in the corner on your right  and put the knife in there then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife in the drawer.

high_descs: walk to face counter near stove
pick up butter knife from counter
wash and remove knife from sink
turn right to face lower cabinets and drawers
